N = randint(3, 8)
plot --> split(y){~1 : base | ~(N * 3) : floors(0) | ~1 : roof}
floors(i) : i < N --> split(y){~3 : floor | ~0.5 : band | ~(N * 3) : floors(i + 1)}
floors(i) : i >= N --> split(y){~3 : floor}
floor --> split(x){~1 : I(column) | ~4 : bay | ~1 : I(column) | ~4 : bay | ~1 : I(column)}
bay --> inset(0.3){I(rect) | I(window3)}
band --> I(rect)
base --> I(rect)
roof --> I(pediment)